{
  "3236960": {
    "name": "皇冠城 Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3236960,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/2fda1379aa4da72fbdb89852d51d63c2.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在可爱的图画中体验丰富的游戏玩法，建设一个中世纪中富有繁荣的美丽城市！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a504d65c3a45f795a11f9ad2667a2b58.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a504d65c3a45f795a11f9ad2667a2b58.webm?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a504d65c3a45f795a11f9ad2667a2b58.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在跟随着一位中世纪后期神圣罗马帝国封建领主主人公的故事中，作为神圣罗马帝国皇帝弗里德里希·冯·哈布斯堡的封臣，以及帝国选帝侯和强大的萨克森公爵的身份，他开发着公国内的未开发领地。<br>在这个过程中，您将面临邻近领地的干扰和阴谋、恶劣的自然环境以及尤其是严寒的冬天带来的困境，还有居民们不断渴望的需求等多种挑战。<br>为了使城市的财政状况富有，您需要开发住房，选择合适的税收政策方案，加工丰富的原材料以高价出口，通过贸易创建一个有利可图的城市！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中，仅开放第一阶段，您只能体验作为神圣罗马帝国萨克森公国封建领主的虚构主人公的旅程。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/79d03c3936a29ed3e73ac4b7da1aaa63.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>城堡区域包括了您计划建造的城堡周围的自然环境和地理！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/5b7eb8752ead2e9154514868734ad7d6.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/7283c08043bb698db852c706e715cce8.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/6d7009a0249fedc43c5a740d31b8275d.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/6d7009a0249fedc43c5a740d31b8275d.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>城堡包括其周围的特定范围，作为城堡区域。该区域包括自然环境和地理、建筑和人口，以及动态的行人流量。<br>根据该区域的自然环境和已建建筑的特性，您可以通过选择更适合周围环境的专门附属设施来提高城堡的产量，并将其转化为科学研究点数或额外的金币收入。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 试玩版中可以选择所有类型的城堡附属设施！</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/fa6b887b3e37004ad4b987553442ca87.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从祈祷室的彩色玻璃到审判所的地下监狱... 考虑城堡的自然环境和建筑来选择您的城堡附属设施！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/c3998b7321930a5d0953de8279888d07.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/2d02f5e1eb2f1d479a837588eeb2bfed.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>城堡附属设施指的是每个城堡可以选择的各种选项。<br>城堡附属设施具有将城堡区域内的自然地理特征、环境瓦片或建筑瓦片、以及人口或行人流量转化为城堡产量的特性。<br>例如，您可能在多石的丘陵地理环境中获得固定的城堡产量奖励，或者对城堡区域内每座图书馆建筑获得额外的产量奖励，或者从海洋或河流等水瓦片中获得整体的额外奖励。<br>根据自然环境和地理特性以及区域内建筑的特性，选择合适的城堡附属设施，以获得更多的益处。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中也能体验全部丰富的自然地理。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/0570c7492b785f6b27fd44042968f112.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造城堡(要塞)和税务局，对住宅进行征税！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/ad982af790465b598ffc746dbdf4fcc8.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>在更高级的住宅中，更富有的居民将缴纳更多的税款。<br>通过建造城堡(要塞)和税务局，向居民们征收居民税吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过设定税收政策，自由组合城市的税收政策！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/bc947369f4d65d6204eca1179eab827b.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>您可以在税收政策选项中自己详细决定各种选项。<br>尝试自由组合各种城市税收政策，通过调整税收选项以实现良好的协同效应！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>房产税好还是人口税好？尝试征收各种特殊税！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a36bc8f1b6899e4d543837b0dc58ed2d.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>您可以征收房产税、人口税、奢侈品税（消费税）、剧院演出税、音乐厅演出税、艺术品交易税以及与自然环境接近有关的各种特殊税。<br>不仅可以征收税款，还可以向生产设施、工业设施和港口设施提供补贴，以缩短生产周期。<br>当资金不足时，可以考虑从银行贷款！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 试玩版中可以选择所有类型的特别税收征收。</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过财务报告摘要了解城市的财务状况！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/1c1c9df8e177994c10c91c88162fa77c.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>游戏的经济系统是各种因素的复杂组合·。了解收入和支出是执行城市财务工作的首要任务。<br>通过财务报告摘要，了解城市财政状况，比较税收管理是否得当，居民税收是否足够，距离要塞太远的建筑是否耗费大量不必要的维护费用，从而更好的管理城市财务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中也可以充分使用财务摘要报告等各种便利功能。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/3d3fcfc146a2af69e61bfe746c58caac.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过贸易出口商品增加收入，或者通过进口获得所需要的商品！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/78e148f296320026a7cc65604fe3f786.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>贸易可以通过城市的整体贸易菜单来接受出口和进口提案，作为异国奢侈品，例如香料如胡椒或稀有的奢侈品如茶叶，可以在每个港口建筑物中进行单独的进口。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中也可以完全使用贸易功能。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/9bb90dbd10ccc9f3084ee77cfc20cf19.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>有时候可能会提出盈利丰厚的特殊出口建议。不要错过城市赚大钱的机会！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>严寒的冬季即将来临。储备冬季资源，做好准备！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/da7caad32347e1e6126690e71be6df75.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/d59f53392a5c44a1a115c01e9b2949c6.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/055f0e061ce002d3ba0329f1b445fd58.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>游戏中有春季、夏季、秋季和冬季四个季节。在冬季，天气会变得更加严寒，需要消耗冬季资源。<br>如果在天暖时没有做好充分的准备，可能会无法度过寒冷的冬天，导致城市崩溃！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中，在提供冬季寒冷的地图上，您可以体验和挑战完整的冬季寒冷。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/87c2653306e9fd52d691ce648d328eba.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>您可以自由选择和指定一个历史上的宗教或从中世纪时代创建的宗教作为国家宗教！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/3e3ba3b1b3d7e30cc8186cbe4f527b21.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/3e3ba3b1b3d7e30cc8186cbe4f527b21.webm?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/3e3ba3b1b3d7e30cc8186cbe4f527b21.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏中共有9种宗教。天主教，新教，归正会，圣公会，东正教，以及爱博雷尔，斯特拉，弗拉马和巫术。您可以为您的领土选择和指定任何宗教作为国家宗教。每个宗教都有自己独特的宗教政策和影响。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中，宗教和国教功能仅部分实现和提供。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/b85c649d558016790c1affae4158141c.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>追随中世纪封建领主的有趣故事，享受完成任务和使命的乐趣！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/45249b7b3b3f45ed0c4d8370d91063e8.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/de5b3c571a5aa92918be80c0649d2e13.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/de5b3c571a5aa92918be80c0649d2e13.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一个巧夺天工的机械工匠发明了活字印刷技术，他是否能在邻近领地的干扰和阴谋中保住这项技术，并大量印刷昂贵的书籍以通过出口赚取丰厚利润，从而解决中世纪城市长期存在的财政赤字问题呢？<br>早于历史的印刷机发明，可能会引发什么样的事件呢？一个故事再次成为另一个有趣故事的原因。<br>另一方面，在葡萄香浓郁的葡萄产区，通过研究和开发出色的葡萄果酱技术，是否能够创建一个以葡萄果酱而闻名的城市呢？<br>建设大学，改进各种研究设施，能否成功地将学术和教育服务转化为收入呢？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 在试玩版中，仅开放第一阶段，您只能体验作为神圣罗马帝国萨克森公国封建领主的虚构主人公的旅程。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/89542d1130663899d21efb8eeb8a524e.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在关卡模式中享受有趣的故事和旅程，或者在随机沙盒模式中享受每个随机产生的自然环境和随机研究技术树的全新创意和深度游戏体验！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/6ca94fcb51f9f9f5937e9eaef8202524.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/6ca94fcb51f9f9f5937e9eaef8202524.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>关卡模式以有趣的故事继续您的游戏旅程，发展您的城市并完成每个阶段的任务。<br>在随机沙盒模式里，通过随机产生的自然环境、研究科技树以及贸易提案等元素，每个游戏都将产生具有经济意义的战略差异，为您带来深度而新颖的游戏体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 试玩版中可以使用随机地图沙盒模式。但是，不提供成就和挑战任务。此外，平衡焦点选择也不提供。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/17382b1a2ecb281b49b9ef5e199caf6f.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>从充满活力，随机产生的科技树中选择与随意的地图相匹配的适当研究任务！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a7cabe245ff7057d04dc7365f128b91f.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a7cabe245ff7057d04dc7365f128b91f.webm?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/a7cabe245ff7057d04dc7365f128b91f.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在随着每场比赛而变化的自然和经济环境中， 做出适当的选择和集中非常重要。在随机产生的科技树中，您需要选择最符合新情境的研究任务！<br>随机产生的科技树每次都会带来新的游戏体验，为经济最优化的选择增添更深层次的沉浸感。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[试玩版通知] 试玩版中提供静态通用科技树和动态生成的随机科技树。</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/e32da8af4436bcf0e5c9c0c93503d7fc.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>中世纪城市模拟建设游戏 -《Crowncity》</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/44d29040ecf23bf422b450575090efbc.poster.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/44d29040ecf23bf422b450575090efbc.webm?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/44d29040ecf23bf422b450575090efbc.mp4?t=1736381635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在《Crowncity》中建设繁荣的中世纪城市吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3236960/extras/599d64eb3c3d9c18467f95c462899c1a.avif?t=1736381635\" width=600 height=76 /></span>",
